{
  "texts": [
    "This collection contains 916 h of EEG data and 23 samples of EEG recordings from 22 people, ages ranging from 1.5 to 22 years.",
    "A continuous EEG readout was acquired following the cessation of anti-seizure medication.",
    "Seizures and non-seizures were identified in 664 EEG files from the CHB-MIT database, which comprised 198 seizures from all patients.",
    "With 129 files involving one or more seizures, these data sets range in duration from one to four hours.",
    "A rate of 256 samples per second was used to record every EEG signal."
  ]
}